<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Government Schemes</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50 p-6 font-sans">
  <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 font-sans max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <header class="mb-6 flex justify-between items-start md:items-center gap-4">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-800">Government Schemes</h2>
        <p class="text-blue-600">Stay updated with latest agricultural schemes and subsidies</p>
      </div>
      <button class="bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-600 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded flex items-center">
        <svg class="h-4 w-4 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m0-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
        Subscribe to Updates
      </button>
    </header>

    <div class="mb-6">
      <div class="relative">
        <svg class="absolute left-3 top-1/2 transform -translate-y-1/2 text-gray-400 h-4 w-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M21 21l-4.35-4.35m0 0A7.5 7.5 0 103.5 10.5a7.5 7.5 0 0013.65 6.15z"/></svg>
        <input type="text" class="pl-10 py-2 border rounded w-full" placeholder="Search schemes...">
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <div class="border rounded-lg shadow hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow overflow-hidden">
        <div class="p-4 space-y-2">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-start">
            <h3 class="text-lg text-blue-800 font-semibold">PM-KISAN Samman Nidhi</h3>
            <div class="flex space-x-2">
              <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 px-2 py-1 text-xs rounded">active</span>
              <span class="bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 px-2 py-1 text-xs rounded">subsidies</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Financial support of ₹6000 per year to small and marginal farmers</p>
          <p class="text-sm"><strong>Amount:</strong> ₹6,000/year</p>
          <p class="text-sm"><strong>Deadline:</strong> 2024-03-31</p>
          <p class="text-sm"><strong>Eligibility:</strong> Small and marginal farmers with landholding up to 2 hectares</p>
          <p class="text-sm"><strong>Documents:</strong> Aadhaar Card, Land Records, Bank Account</p>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center pt-4 border-t">
            <span class="text-xs text-gray-500">Updated: 2024-01-15</span>
            <div class="flex space-x-2">
              <button class="text-blue-600 border border-blue-300 hover:bg-blue-50 px-3 py-1 text-sm rounded">Download</button>
              <button class="bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-600 text-white px-3 py-1 text-sm rounded">Apply Now</button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="border rounded-lg shadow hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow overflow-hidden">
        <div class="p-4 space-y-2">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-start">
            <h3 class="text-lg text-blue-800 font-semibold">Pradhan Mantri Fasal Bima Yojana</h3>
            <div class="flex space-x-2">
              <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 px-2 py-1 text-xs rounded">active</span>
              <span class="bg-purple-100 text-purple-800 px-2 py-1 text-xs rounded">insurance</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Crop insurance scheme providing financial support to farmers</p>
          <p class="text-sm"><strong>Amount:</strong> Up to ₹2,00,000</p>
          <p class="text-sm"><strong>Deadline:</strong> 2024-04-15</p>
          <p class="text-sm"><strong>Eligibility:</strong> All farmers growing notified crops</p>
          <p class="text-sm"><strong>Documents:</strong> Land Records, Sowing Certificate, Bank Account</p>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center pt-4 border-t">
            <span class="text-xs text-gray-500">Updated: 2024-01-20</span>
            <div class="flex space-x-2">
              <button class="text-blue-600 border border-blue-300 hover:bg-blue-50 px-3 py-1 text-sm rounded">Download</button>
              <button class="bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-600 text-white px-3 py-1 text-sm rounded">Apply Now</button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
